{
  "chapter": 72,
  "chapter_summary": "第72章\"峰回路转\"讲述了小鱼儿、轩辕三光、江玉郎在山洞中遭遇五个黑衣人的经历。这些黑衣人是无牙门下士，专门捕食老鼠，令众人惊恐不已。江玉郎试图挑拨黑衣人对付小鱼儿，但小鱼儿机智应对。关键时刻，花无缺及时出现，以\"移花接玉\"功夫制服黑衣人。然而黑衣人因害怕回去受罚，纷纷服毒自尽。花无缺放走了江玉郎，小鱼儿对此颇有微词。本章展现了小鱼儿的机智、花无缺的武功高强，以及无牙门的诡异恐怖。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你若想以慕容九妹来要挟我，你就错了。你莫非不知道她老是想要我的命，我又怎会要救她？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老子早就对女人没兴趣，她的死活，更和老子没关系。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，两位为何不向我出手呀？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老子并不想宰你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "吃大便的朋友，我杀你还怕脏了手哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，在下就要告退了，这位慕容姑娘，自然也要跟着在下走的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你走吧！你带走了慕容九妹，还怕没有人找你算账。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这倒不劳阁下费心，若有人问起我来，我便说带走慕容姑娘，只为的是怕她遭了你的毒手，若不是江小鱼，慕容九妹此刻又怎会变成如此模样。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "有其父必有其子，你们父子两人，别的本事没有，栽赃耍赖，混充好人的本事，倒真还没有别人比得上。但你抢了段合肥的银子，事实俱在，你总赖不掉的吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "什么银子，我两手空空，哪里有银子？现在银子是谁的，就是谁动手抢去的，这道理岂非更简单了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你龟儿子想赖起老子来了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你说我赖你，我就说你赖我，咱们倒不妨看看，江湖中人是相信你‘恶赌鬼’的话，还是相信我江玉郎的话。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你龟儿子若早生几年，‘十大恶人’哪里还有老子的份。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "过奖过奖，在下只不过……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "来的人既能使你手下发出这样的惨呼，必定可怕得很，你要出去送死没关系，但慕容九妹……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友们是什么人？干什么来的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九秀山庄的九姑娘和‘恶赌鬼’全都在这里，朋友们若是识相，还是快快退出去吧，再迟想走也走不了啦！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "老鼠……笼子里好多老鼠。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，老鼠，在下五人此来找的只是老鼠，与人无关，各位只要站着不动，在下等必定秋毫无犯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "捉老鼠干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "敝上非鼠肉不欢，是以令在下等四处搜捕，但此间方圆百里内的老鼠都已流窜入山，是以在下等才一路追捕过来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪这山洞里老鼠特别多，原来就是被他们赶来的，我本来还以为外面来了只恶猫哩。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "朋友们的主子是谁？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这喜欢吃老鼠的朋友是谁，你知道么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我如今才知道，老鼠竟如此可怕。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "格老子，成千成百只耗子，看起来真和十只八只差得多了，四川耗子虽多，但老子也没有看过有这么多的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下倒不是害怕，只不过觉得有些恶心。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位朋友说的不错，老鼠非但不可怕，而且还美味得很。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "美味？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若不信，一试便知。",
      "tone": "怪笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "君子不夺人所好，老鼠既是如此美味，还是留给阁下自用吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "可惜可惜，想不到阁下看来胆子虽大，却连只老鼠都不敢吃，否则阁下尝过老鼠肉之后，再吃别的肉就味同嚼蜡了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "朋友既然已找到了老鼠，此刻总该走了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你素来最爱多管闲事，这次怎地不管了？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "若有人喜欢吃老鼠，那是自己的事，我为何要管？正如你喜欢吃大便，我也是管不了的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "朋友真要走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "在下早已说过，此来只是为了老鼠，与人无干。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "难道朋友就不知道，这里有比老鼠更好的东西么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "本门弟子，都觉得女人不如老鼠可爱……",
      "tone": "怪笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "金银珠宝难道也不比老鼠可爱么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "金银珠宝？在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "有这两位在此，我不敢说。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我真奇怪，以前为何不早把你宰了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "就凭你要杀我，只怕还不容易。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "后面没有老鼠，各位还是请回吧！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "朋友最好知道，你虽不敢吃老鼠，老鼠却敢吃你的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "我已有好几天没洗澡了，肉脏得很，老鼠只怕也吃不下去。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，你这人有趣得很，而且胆子也不小……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "朋友还不知道，我虽然对老鼠有些头疼，但人，我却是不怕的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "老鼠既不认得我，我也不认得老鼠，你们就算把天下的老鼠都捉去吃光，我也不管你们，但你们若想打别的主意，我却要不客气了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不来惹咱们，咱们也不惹你，但你若想挡咱们的去路，咱们却要不客气了！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "轩辕三光，你还不来帮忙么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "轩辕三光你既已猜出我等是何人门下，你还敢出手？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "轩辕三光，你难道也像女人，怕老鼠？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "自命为天下第一聪明的人，竟连老鼠也对付不了……江小鱼，你几时想到过你会死在老鼠手里。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在没有想到过……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花无缺，想不到你居然来了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "朋友是谁？为何来多管闲事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你纵不认得我，也该认得这手功夫吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "移……移花接玉！既有移花宫的人到此，在下等只有告退。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你们弄了我一身老鼠屎，此刻就想走么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这话只怕还轮不到阁下来说，就凭阁下……哼！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "你们瞧他不起？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "既是如此，莫要老鼠帮忙，你们不妨和他打一场，五人齐上也无妨，我绝不出手。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只要阁下不出手，这小子……",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "各位此刻已知道他的厉害了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到人竟不如老鼠，竟如此禁不得打。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "我现在手已不痒了，还不快站起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_ren",
      "text": "五个这么大的人，居然还好意思赖在地上，难道还要等你们师娘来，抱你们起来么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他们只怕永远也站不起来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这五人挨了两拳，难道就气得自杀了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他们也许是以为你放不过他们，所以自己先就……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他们就算弄了我一身老鼠屎，我也不会杀他们的呀！这些人难道是老鼠吃多了，人也变得像老鼠一样想不开？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些龟儿子说死就死，死得倒真快。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "是呀，难道他们嘴里早就含着毒药，随时都准备死不成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说的不错，这些杂种竟是将毒药藏在牙齿里的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "但他们为什么要自杀呢？我既没有杀他们的意思，也不想逼问他们的口供，他们难道真是活得不耐烦了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你想不通的事，回答就在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无牙门下士，可杀不可辱……这算什么见鬼的意思？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这意思就是叫他们打不过别人时，赶快自杀，免得丢他们主子的人，他们现在若不自杀，回去死得只怕更要惨十倍。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你是说他们怕回去受主子的酷刑，所以宁可现在自杀，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "但他们在这里挨揍，他们的主子根本不知道呀，只要他们自己不说，难道我还会说出去不成。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这些龟儿子也许正是以小人之心，度君子之腹，以为你……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不是这原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你说是什么原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我瞧见他们时，他们本有七个人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "这就对了！他们五个人进来，还留着两个人躲在暗处，那两人见势不妙，恐怕已暗中溜了。这五人算定他们回去一定要报告的，与其到那时凌迟受罪，倒不如现在落个痛快的好。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你进来时，没有瞧见那两个人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我听见你的呼喊声，立刻就闯了进来，并没有去留意别的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，我们竟被这些鬼老鼠弄晕了头，五六个大活人从我们身边溜走，我们竟全都不知道。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，那姓江的小杂种，果然溜了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你进来时，我还瞧见他的，那时他脸上像是还有欢喜之色，以为你要来宰我，后来想必是一发现情况有点不对，就立刻开溜……唉，这小子一向是个鬼精灵。我本该特别盯着他才是的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他自己走了倒也好。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你是早已瞧见他的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好像瞟过一眼。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但你还是放他走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我和他总算交友一场……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但你为何要让他将慕容九妹一起带走呢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    }
